  <!-- PAGE HERO -->
  <section class="pg-hero">
    <h1>Magnesium Glycinate vs Citrate for Sleep</h1>
    <p class="pg-sub">Magnesium is one of the most researched minerals for sleep support, but the form you choose determines whether you get a restful night or a trip to the bathroom. We break down the clinical evidence, absorption pathways, side effects, and practical recommendations for magnesium glycinate versus citrate so you can make the right choice for your sleep goals.</p>
